{"tid":1238111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩入一入黎研究下 意志堅定既人可以考警察！","createTime":"2019-06-17T16:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T17:37:39.000Z","uid":15309,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebf2aa999108847d98ab1bbad379a5d3274f4e1","tid":1238111,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"唔好負皮住 睇清楚先！<br />\n其實依家可以搵一班意志堅定既人一齊考警察<br />\n點解？ 當有下一次大型遊行示威既時候<br />\n或者衝突既時候 就係呢班新加入既警察做野既時候<br />\n到時佢地係前線一齊除低裝備企係示威者前面<br />\n你地覺得個效果會幾咁壯觀？幾咁有用<br />\n直頭可以打擊政府，警察士氣<br />\n仲可以令到個示威昇華去另一個層次<br />\n不過首先要班人頂得順中間個過程可能會比朋友鬧<br />\n比警方洗腦<br />\n但為左香港既將來<br />\n不如齊齊考警察 創造一個奇蹟出黎<br />\n呢步暗棋要靠大家一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果覺得唔可行請屌細力啲 <br />\n我仲要去發夢 <br />\n各位共勉之"},{"pid":"b08b50e2e2d7988822e430d8c1a2fd6ee9be38d2","tid":1238111,"uid":24910,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"你真係On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e600f9192284d2ca6f06d8abc0a8b6be4413f2","tid":1238111,"uid":203251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9da7f8375ba1696c8ec09e959f9a7528a8d68a","tid":1238111,"uid":12827,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"雨傘都有人咁講<br />\n結果呢？"},{"pid":"6775170ef61238fd8e7febd5326cab82b58135b9","tid":1238111,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769fb9a62bf48d162fcc8b5c66f5a8d5a27c4aa3","tid":1238111,"uid":120537,"like":9,"